1) Employee with highest salary

**Aim: To find employee(s) earning highest salary.** \
Requirement: Employee table.\
Theory: Subquery returns max value.\
Query: SELECT ename
FROM employee
WHERE sal = (SELECT MAX(sal) FROM employee);
