2) Highest paid clerk

**Aim: To find clerk earning highest salary.** \
Requirement: Job and salary columns.\
Query: SELECT empno, ename
FROM employee
WHERE job='CLERK'
AND sal = (SELECT MAX(sal) FROM employee WHERE job='CLERK');
