6) Highest salary in each department

**Aim: To find highest paid employee per department.** \
Requirement: Deptno and salary.\
Theory: Correlated subquery.\
Query: SELECT ename, deptno, sal
FROM employee e
WHERE sal = (
  SELECT MAX(sal)
  FROM employee
  WHERE deptno = e.deptno
);
