10) Job groups with total salary > managers

**Aim: To find jobs whose total salary exceeds manager salary.** \
Requirement: Employee table.\
Theory: GROUP BY + HAVING with subquery.\
Query: SELECT job
FROM employee
GROUP BY job
HAVING SUM(sal) > (
  SELECT MAX(sal)
  FROM employee
  WHERE job='MANAGER'
);
